OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FAs journalists we are always aware of
OL,7,Fhyperbole or exaggerations, but for an
OL,8,Findependent regulator is hugely
OL,9,Fsignificant.
OL,11,FThe Government have acted off the back
OL,12,Fof a wide consultation with supporters
OL,13,Fin the wake of the failed attempt by
OL,14,Fthe most powerful clubs in England, ,
OL,15,Fwhich brought huge protests across the
OL,16,Fcountry and threatened to destabilise
OL,17,Fthe English game.
