OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FThere have been concerns for some time
OL,7,Fthat the way football is managed in
OL,8,Fthe country - and that includes fans
OL,9,Fin the Midlands - is not in the best
OL,10,Finterests of supporters who are
OL,11,Fmarginalised and left on the bench,
OL,12,Fwhile having to put up with unpopular
OL,13,Fdecisions as their club lurches from
OL,14,Fone crisis to another.
OL,16,FThe legislation is designed to give
OL,17,Ffans more of a say and is important as
OL,18,Fit means clubs can't change key
OL,19,Fsentiments like badges, kit colours or
OL,20,Fmove the club away without going to
OL,21,Fthe fans first.
