OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FI should point out that numerous clubs
OL,7,Fhave made those changes without
OL,8,Flistening to fans and the mistrust and
OL,9,Fbitterness continues even now, years
OL,10,Fafter.
OL,12,FAn independent regulator will be set
OL,13,Fto look after the top five leagues in
OL,14,Fthe country and it could be the one to
OL,15,Fgovern finances, deal with appropriate
OL,16,Fpunishments for financial
OL,17,Firregularities, and have more
OL,18,Fstringent tests for prospective owners
OL,19,Fto pass.
