OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FIn the Midlands, and have been duly
OL,7,Fpunished for breaking financial
OL,8,Fregulations with point deductions by
OL,9,Fboth the English Football League and
OL,10,Fthe Premier League respectively.
OL,12,FThe rival supporters have at least one
OL,13,Fthing in common - their disdain for
OL,14,Fboth organisations.
OL,16,FAs such, a regulator will be widely
OL,17,Fwelcomed.
