OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FThe English Football League which
OL,7,Flooks after the Championship, League
OL,8,FOne and League Two and the Premier
OL,9,FLeague have rarely seen eye to eye - a
OL,10,Fsimmering tension since clubs resigned
OL,11,Fen masse to join the Premier League as
OL,12,Fyou guessed it, a breakaway league in
OL,13,F1992 which allowed clubs a greater say
OL,14,Fover TV revenue.
OL,16,FOnly recently, have criticised the
OL,17,FPremier League for dragging their
OL,18,Fheels and failing to find an agreement
OL,19,Fover EFL funding, which the Football
OL,20,FLeague needs to help clubs survive.
