OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FFor those who aren't aware of the
OL,7,Fcomplexities, all leagues are
OL,8,Fconnected via the football pyramid
OL,9,Fwhich means in essence a village team
OL,10,Fcan gain multiple promotions through
OL,11,Ftheir local leagues, to the EFL and
OL,12,Fthen the
OL,14,FBoth control the top four divisions in
OL,15,Fthe country but it is an irony that
OL,16,Fthe breakaway league of 1992 is
OL,17,Fhelping to fund the division it left
OL,18,Fbehind.
