OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FThis means that the EFL have
OL,7,Fcautiously welcomed a regulator, a
OL,8,Fhint that suggests the Premier League
OL,9,Fhas too much power.
OL,11,FUnsurprisingly, the Premier League is
OL,12,Fless keen, who may see it as a threat
OL,13,Fto their independence and the ability
OL,14,Fof clubs in the league to make their
OL,15,Fown decisions.
OL,17,FThat's not to say that it's the good
OL,18,Fguys vs the bad guys.
