OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FAs mentioned previously in the
OL,7,FMidlands, there's not much love for
OL,8,Feither organisation - supporters from
OL,9,Fand Derby County say they've suffered
OL,10,Funder previous ownership and been
OL,11,Fpunished for it, while and Forest will
OL,12,Ffeel aggrieved about any points
OL,13,Fdeductions or fines because of
OL,14,Fperceived financial failures.
OL,16,FThe fact that two Premier League sides
OL,17,Fhave had points deducted and that the
OL,18,Fusual clubs seem to be promoted and
OL,19,Frelegated season after season, point
OL,20,Ftowards a broken model and fans are
OL,21,Ffed up of being sidelined.
