OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FFor clubs like Darlington, Bury and
OL,7,FScarborough who went out of business,
OL,8,Fthis regulation has come far too late.
OL,10,FHad the same happened to Derby - and
OL,11,Fit was close - we might have seen the
OL,12,Fend of the EFL as we know it. Instead
OL,13,Fthis legislation's aim is preserve
OL,14,Fheritage and ensure long-term
OL,15,Ffinancial stability for clubs.
OL,17,FQuite how that will be implemented is
OL,18,Funclear but huge gulfs exist between
OL,19,FEFL clubs and their richer cousins in
OL,20,Fthe Premier League.
