OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FIt's why the regulator will also have
OL,7,Fthe power to make sure both
OL,8,Forganisations reach an agreement over
OL,9,Fmoney when there's an impasse, and
OL,10,Fperhaps that's another fear of the top
OL,11,Fflight.
OL,13,FIt has to be noted that neither
OL,14,Forganisation has come out well in
OL,15,Fthis. Instead, it's the Government who
OL,16,Fhave taken matters into their own
OL,17,Fhands after listening to supporters,
OL,18,Fwho have had enough.
