OL,3,CFootball Governance Bill - what will
OL,4,Cit mean for clubs in the Midlands ?
OL,6,FConcerns over 'unscrupulous owners'
OL,7,Fhave continued, with supporters seeing
OL,8,Fpoints being taken away. Fans will say
OL,9,Fthis huge change is long overdue - a
OL,10,Fforced change which would not have
OL,11,Fhappened otherwise.
OL,13,FIn 2021 after clubs U-turned on the
OL,14,FSuper League, the-then Prime Minister
OL,15,FBoris Johnson vowed to stop any other
OL,16,Fteam even entertaining the idea. Three
OL,17,Fyears later, fans have that and more.
